vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding the application for and approval of the fill permit and removal of the floodplain (FP) prefix from approximately 0.11 acres of the current 0.40 acres of floodplain located at 2850 Dairy Milk Lane, within the floodplain of West Fork of Joes Creek, Fill Permit 21-03 - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
